==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''shepherd moon'''
# A small [[moon]] that [[orbit]]s near the outer edges of a [[planetary ring]] or within gaps in the ring. The edge of the ring [[remain]]s sharply defined owing to the [[gravity]] of shepherd moons.

===Synonyms===
*[[shepherd satellite]]

